# Credentials. Never, under any circumstance.
06 Code/spacetrack_auth.json
**/spacetrack_auth.json
*.env
.env

# The archive. ~2 MB a day forever, and it is data, not source - putting it in
# git would make every clone enormous and every commit slow. It is also the one
# thing here that genuinely cannot be regenerated, so back it up separately.
06 Code/supgp_archive/
06 Code/output/*.csv

# Environments and caches
06 Code/.venv-meeting/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
06 Code/splid-devkit/

# Rendered audio - regenerable from the .txt scripts beside them
06 Code/*.mp3

# Obsidian's own state
.obsidian/workspace*.json
.obsidian/cache
.trash/
